title: Ep 17: The Last Episode? Ft. Aurora
description:
Today's Proceedings:  A very special guest joins us this week as the wed Erika and Christian discuss relationships with the new couple of Josh and Aurora!  We discuss the timeline of dating from using dating apps in the year 2020 all the way to falling out of love with your partner, as all relationships go!

Rate and Review our podcast and share it with your friends!
